    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "A very Happy Birthday...... July 1967.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "I am very Lucky to have the opportunity this afternoon to be",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "able to introduce to you the ufo contact igap journal. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "magazine has been dedicated to Mr. George Adamski.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "My letter to you and the enclosed magazine is a project of my",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "own. I am a reporter for ufo contact, and in this way I hope to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "bring to the attention of V.I.P of our country, our magazine and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "the message that it contains, to the reader. I don't sell the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "magazine, but plan to give it to the person I write to as a gift.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "The cost is my own, and the experience I will gain will be my",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "reward, perhaps an advancement to the position of co-worker for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "IGAP in the future.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Thank you very much for giving me a moment of your time. I am",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "sure you will find our magazine interesting.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
